name: Rhiannon Schilling
text: For $11.76 I was able to pick up a large pizza with pepperoni, mushrooms, and sausage. That's a great price, and they did not skimp out on the toppings at all. The girl at the counter was super nice and we got a free movie rental for next door. Can't beat that!

name: Shawn A
text: Weird location attached to Family Video renting stores.  Pizza and a movie sound good in place of Netflix?üòè

name: Charis Ditamore
text: Marco's has the best pizza in town! Service is always great, food is always fantastic and on time. Their menu has a ton of options to choose from and the staff is always polite and friendly. They really go above and beyond.

name: Fernando Acosta
text: Best pizza because of its weekly deals combined with the amount of flavor is unmatched.

name: Frank Oros
text: Always made well. Good grade sausage, well seasoned.

name: Erin Orchard
text: Edit 03/11/2018. Another terrible dine-in experience. Went tonight. Called in the order beforehand. Said DINE IN. Parmesan crust. Had coupon for free pizza (after 9 visits). Got there and said I couldn't use the coupon... the NEXT one was ‚Ä¶More

name: Kayla Chamberlin
text: The pizza here is amazing!!! Great service too! Definitely a five star rating!!!

name: Ernestine Woodard
text: The food is delicious and service excellent!

name: Bob Stoltman
text: Best pizza in the quad city's
